TITLE: Episode 136 - "What is the Gospel?" with Cody Cook
DESCRIPTION: Easter is coming. What does that mean? What is "the Gospel?" How is it good news to hear of a man's death? How could someone come back from death? What does this story mean? Join us as we talk to our buddy Cody about the gospel itself and what the good news really is.
